{{Redirect|Chilca}}
'''Chilca''' was a [[rocket launch site]] in [[Peru]] at {{coord|12|30|S|76|48|W|}},  near [[Lima]]. Chilca was in service from 1974 and 1983 and was mainly used for launching [[Arcas (rocket)|Arcas]] and [[Project Nike|Nike]] [[sounding rocket|sounding rockets]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.astronautix.com/sites/chilca.htm|title=Chilca|work=[[Encyclopedia Astronautica]]|accessdate=16 August 2014}}</ref>

